<Layout title="Web Design by Aidxn Design">



  <ContainerFW>
    <SectionEmail>
      <Fragment slot="title">
        Web Design by Aidxn.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        Highly awarded web designer on the Gold Coast. From Wordpress to Shopify to Web3 JS languages, we have you covered. Specialising in building blazing-fast, custom web experiences that drive sales through unique creative marketing. 
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="cover">
        <Picture
                  src={PagecoverHero}
                  sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 2000px, 1000px"
                  widths={[1000, 1500, 2000]}
                  aspectRatio="3:2"
                  background="#f2f2f2"
                  fit="cover"
                  position="center"
                  class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                />
      </Fragment>
    </SectionEmail>

  </ContainerFW>

  <ContainerXL>
    <SectionHeadImg>
      <Fragment slot="title">
        Shopify Plus optimisation.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        We've worked in web design and development for over 10 years, if you're 
        looking for someone you can honestly trust with your Shopify Plus store, 
        we're worth giving a call. Velocity even comes in RubyonRails for use as 
        a Shopify theme. (Shopify theme available to Moonshot customers only)
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="cover">
        <Picture
                  src={Pagecover}
                  sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 2000px, 1000px"
                  widths={[1000, 1500, 2000]}
                  aspectRatio="3:2"
                  background="#f2f2f2"
                  fit="cover"
                  position="center"
                  class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                />
      </Fragment>
    </SectionHeadImg>
  </ContainerXL>

  <ContainerXL>
    <SectionHeadSecImg>
      <Fragment slot="title">
        Wordpress optimisation.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        We're absolutely nuts about perfect web performance, after all, it's what the customer demands. 
        If your business is locked into a Web2 stack like Wordpress we have plenty of experience optimising 
        these sites with great results. From code structure improvement to waterfall optimisation, 
        we comb through your site constantly as new content arrives, always keeping your site fast and ranking well.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="cover">
        <Picture
                  src={PagecoverSecondary}
                  sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 2000px, 1000px"
                  widths={[1000, 1500, 2000]}
                  aspectRatio="3:2"
                  background="#f2f2f2"
                  fit="cover"
                  position="center"
                  class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                />
      </Fragment>
    </SectionHeadSecImg>
  </ContainerXL>

  <ContainerXL>
    <GallerySlider />
  </ContainerXL>

  <ContainerXL>
    <SectionTextarea>
      <Fragment slot="title">Need a custom web experience?</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        Our favourite thing to hear is a brand that wants to go truly "Banksy" on their online prescence. 
        Trust us when we say we've seen creative e-commerce design pay off time and time again. 
        We've worked with a number of international market, global brands to create true digital art, 
        that truly drives sales. Using game theory and 3D interation to hook your customer with ease.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="cover">
        <Picture
                  src={CoverTextarea}
                  sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 2000px, 1000px"
                  widths={[1000, 1500, 2000]}
                  aspectRatio="3:2"
                  background="#f2f2f2"
                  fit="cover"
                  position="center"
                  class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                />
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="iconleft">
        <Icon class="w-16 h-16" name="simple-icons:threedotjs" />
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="titleleft">
        Three.JS
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="textleft">
        Our absolute favourite website framework when it comes to getting creative is Three.JS.
        If you've got 3D assets within your brand already that aren't being put to use online, 
        you and your customer are missing out big time!
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="iconright">
        <Icon class="w-16 h-16" name="simple-icons:astro" />
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="titleright">
        Astro.JS
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="textright">
        We write all our code within an Astro-based framework to ensure the fastest possible pageload times, 
        while also giving us to almost magical ability to work with any framework or code language you need.
        Integrate a React or Vue component? No problemo. Back-end API's in any language? Already sorted.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="iconleft2">
        <Icon class="w-16 h-16" name="simple-icons:cinema4d" />
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="titleleft2">
        Cinema4D
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="textleft2">
        Taking your custom experience further towards the metaverse with 
        high-quality 3D asset creation using Cinema4D, the industry leader 
        in rendering and 3D design. Made even more powerful with code.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="iconright2">
        <Icon class="w-16 h-16" name="simple-icons:stripe" />
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="titleright2">
        Stripe payments
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="textright2">
        Streamline your payment process and boost sales with Stripe's 
        secure payment gateway. With one-click checkout, you can 
        provide a seamless payment experience for your customers, 
        reducing cart abandonment and driving conversions. Benefit 
        from Stripe's transparent pricing, and robust fraud prevention 
        from day one for your business. For frictionless payment experiences.
      </Fragment>      
    </SectionTextarea>

