  </ContainerXL>

  <Container>

    <Sectionhead>
      <Fragment slot="title">Introducing Velocity7.</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        Helping businesses stay on the edge of competition in the most competitive industries. 
        The fastest website framework developed specifically for Australian businesses, and the 
        web performance issues we individually face. Out-performing some of the biggest names in 
        tech in our <a href="#">pageload comparisons</a>. Works with any framework, infinitely extendable.
      </Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>
  </Container>

